            "body": "<p>try this:<br><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Integer&gt; index = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nList&lt;String&gt; five_names = new ArrsyList&lt;&gt;();\nList&lt;String&gt; allnames = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>store  five random values<br><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>for(int i = 0;i &lt; 5;i++){\n\n  int index_no = getrandomNumber();\n  index.add(index_no);\n  five_names.add(allnames.get(index_no));\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>getRandomNumber method:<br><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public int getRandomNumber(){\n\n    Random rnd = new Random();\n    int x = rnd.nextInt(20);\n\n    if(index.contains(x)){\n       return getRandomNumber();\n    }else{\n       return x\n    }\n }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
